{"tid":51121,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"【強國又抄】上海驚見山寨版 日本「大江戶溫泉物語」急澄清","createTime":"2016-12-23T03:18:53.000Z","updateTime":"2016-12-25T14:19:27.000Z","uid":48093,"like":0,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"79e51ddb66e6ec5658d53610718c0a48b57af031","tid":51121,"uid":48093,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-23T03:18:53.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"http://static.apple.nextmedia.com/images/e-paper/20161223/large/1482458338_8b82.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fstatic.apple.nextmedia.com%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20161223%2Flarge%2F1482458338_8b82.jpg&h=14169b72&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n日本東京台場的「大江戶溫泉物語」向來是熱門浸溫泉的旅遊地點，亦深受中國遊客歡迎，但近日中國上海驚現同名設施，日本「大江戶溫泉物語」於周四澄清在中國並無分號，強調公司與上海的設施並無任何關聯。<br />\n<br />\n這間位於上海市郊、名為「大江戶溫泉物語」的溫泉設施周三起試業，有同名微博聲稱日本的大江戶溫泉物語落戶上海。除了浸浴之外，更提供餐飲及按摩服務。宣傳單張介紹設施內設有熊本熊大江戶「專賣店」、時租客房，以及「福祿壽之湯」人工溫泉。<br />\n<br />\n從外觀來看，「山寨版」無論是建築風格、招牌字體以至門口標語，都幾乎與台場的「大江戶溫泉物語」一模一樣。設施內擺放大批疑似熊本縣吉祥物「熊本熊」的展示品、店內的指示夾雜簡體字及日文，強調日本風情。試業一日後，周四晚已吸引大批顧客入場光顧。<br />\n<br />\n日本「大江戶溫泉物語」周四表示，公司未有在海外設立分支，亦無與其他海外企業合作，強調與上海「大江戶溫泉物語」絕無關聯。<br />\n上海「大江戶溫泉物語」的職員指：「雖然不知道與日本公司的關係，但認為在上海營業並無問題。」"},{"pid":"533087ef0103017339030816fd45fc457d0ce402","tid":51121,"uid":10635,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-23T03:22:11.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2016/12/23/112210_105c77cd33c1c23a8b6c69377a062c6e.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2016%2F12%2F23%2F112210_105c77cd33c1c23a8b6c69377a062c6e.jpg&h=21b04b24&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"64b93655f68181300757ba49c128bfe7ba14c064","tid":51121,"uid":25556,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-23T03:22:24.000Z","msg":"屌你啦小日本<br />\n支那呢個先係正版呀<br />\n唔信你試下告唔告得入<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cd85db1066c151c39841799ee43a0920fd1abacb","tid":51121,"uid":42550,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-23T03:24:11.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: red;\">強調日本風情。試業一日後，周四晚已吸引大批顧客入場光顧。</span>"},{"pid":"0bd98d9c74d521f8adf43737231b7d4f4ab671e4","tid":51121,"uid":10707,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-23T03:27:08.000Z","msg":"小小支那，可笑可笑<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0a43794ca4fe60526720e26d086dde59a283f13c","tid":51121,"uid":5715,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-23T03:28:36.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><span style=\"color: red;\">強調日本風情。試業一日後，周四晚已吸引大批顧客入場光顧。</span></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n抗日喎，民族仇恨喎，支那人正垃圾<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"01f21d05c5bcac19719646f46bc31fdf6cbb34b6","tid":51121,"uid":38523,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-23T03:33:45.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><span style=\"color: red;\">強調日本風情。試業一日後，周四晚已吸引大批顧客入場光顧。</span></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n抗日喎，民族仇恨喎，支那人正垃圾<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n世上有冇人可以廢得過支那人<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c2ee55686f9fea8d2943181fffc0f37f4fa9af62","tid":51121,"uid":8347,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-23T04:49:05.000Z","msg":"垃圾支那人<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n山寨大國"},{"pid":"0cd334ec58c515580f3098ec4cbc3694f4db314e","tid":51121,"uid":60831,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-23T04:51:11.000Z","msg":"諗起成班蝗係池入面柯尿<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3a3a7e07ed3df45d11ad781aba3062b72a86a08b","tid":51121,"uid":55513,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-23T04:56:03.000Z","msg":"戇鳩鳩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"p